## Before shipping an update

1. Every description is **≤ 100 words** (enforced in `build_opportunities.py`).
2. Deadlines match listing text; flag “verify on official site” when OFY is the only source.
3. No ineligible or closed calls in the main Opportunities sheet.
4. Gender category is set on every row.
5. Excel saves successfully (close open workbook if Windows reports permission denied; Excel lock files `~$*` are disposable).

The tracker should let the team quickly see **priority, fit, gender category, and deadlines** for proposal efforts.
